# MadSpin cascade for FCNC single-top + Higgs.
# Decays the single top inclusively (t > b W, W > all), reproducing the
# inline thFCNC_utHyy_tphi sample (lep lep + j j W lines = W inclusive).
# Placeholders (SEED_PLACEHOLDER, EVENTS_PLACEHOLDER) are filled per chunk
# by the Madgraph task before MadSpin is launched.
set spinmode madspin
set seed SEED_PLACEHOLDER
import EVENTS_PLACEHOLDER
decay t > b w+, w+ > all all
decay t~ > b~ w-, w- > all all
launch
